stimulus:
Welcome to the experiment


Press any key to begin.

In each trial, you will see two different images sourced from a popular social platform.

Each image will have an upvote count above it.

An upvote is a like given by users of the platform and helps promote quality content and discussion on the platform.

A higher upvote count means more people like the post and recommend it to other users.


Press any key to continue.

An upvote is a like given by users of the platform and helps promote quality content and discussion on the platform.

A higher upvote count means more people like the post and recommend it to other users.


Press any key to continue.

At the start of every trial, both images will be blurred.

The image you select will unblur itself, and the other one will stay the same.

Please take some time to consider both images and their upvote counts. If you respond too fast, you will not see the image.
